49
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:09,110
You're a real general.

50
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,830
How odd you go back on your word!

51
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:12,720
Miss,

52
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,000
